    <p>
        This <a target="_blank" href="https://www.syncfusion.com/aspnet-mvc-ui-controls/charts/chart-types/range-column-chart" aria-label="ASP.NET MVC Range Column Chart">ASP.NET MVC Range Column Chart<span class="sr-only">opens in a new tab</span></a> example demonstrates the Range Column series, highlighting the maximum and minimum temperature changes in the Contiguous U.S. for the year 2024 over different months.
